Data-Formatter-Html version 0.01
================================

This module that converts Perl data structures into HTML code, 
formatting the data nicely for presentation to a human.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 Attribute::Abstract
 Scalar::Util
 List::MoreUtils

